OL,6,GStrike action by members of the
OL,7,GNational Union of Journalists has
OL,8,Gaffected regional BBC TV news
OL,9,Gprogrammes for a second day.
OL,11,FThe 24-hour strike by BBC Local staff
OL,12,Fin England began at 11am yesterday
OL,13,Fand affected lunchtime, early evening
OL,14,Fand late-evening regional TV news
OL,15,Fprogrammes in most English regions,
OL,16,Fas well as live output on many local
OL,17,Fradio stations.
OL,3,CBBC strike affects early morning TV
OL,4,Cnews bulletins
