OL,6,FOn television, the early morning
OL,7,Fregional news programmes within BBC
OL,8,FBreakfast today were replaced by an
OL,9,Fall-England news service, produced by
OL,10,Fthe news operation in Salford.
OL,12,FWhilst many regions took the
OL,13,Fbulletins produced in Salford,
OL,14,Fviewers in the East Midlands, the
OL,15,FSouth East and the West did receive
OL,16,Ftheir usual dedicated bulletins.
OL,18,FThe NUJ opposes the BBC's plans to
OL,19,Fmerge some local radio programmes in
OL,20,FEngland.  The union says this would
OL,21,F"undermine already hollowed out local
OL,22,Fradio content across England".
OL,3,CBBC strike affects early morning TV
